text:
I am try to write some hubl logic to display a &lt;a href&gt; link only if specific fields of the author are filled out, so here is my code but it always seems to render the &lt;a href&gt; even when all those fields are empty for authors that I know do not have them filled:

```{% if content.blog_author.title &amp;&amp; content blog_author.image === 0 %}
                           &lt;span&gt; By: {{ content.blog_post_author.display_name }}&lt;/span&gt;
                        {% else %}
                            &lt;span&gt;By: &lt;a
                                href="https://{{request.domain}}/{{ group.slug }}/author/{{ content.blog_post_author.slug }}"&gt;
                                {{ content.blog_post_author.display_name }}
                            &lt;/a&gt;
                            &lt;/span&gt;
                        {% endif %}```
